        "timestamp": "2018-08-29 20:11:25.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 3:\n\nI missed the secondary helm-verify – so the procedure for merging after talking with Mike and Mandeep\n\tLet the jobbuilder kick in – it runs the helm verify – then merge the code\n\tIn this case patchset 3 was committed – helm verify [master level] ran OK\n\nhttps://gerrit.onap.org/r/#/c/61111/3\nhttps://jenkins.onap.org/job/oom-master-verify-helm/182/\n14:20:59 [pomba]\n14:20:59 make[1]: Entering directory '/w/workspace/oom-master-verify-helm/kubernetes'\n14:20:59 Hang tight while we grab the latest from your chart repositories...\n14:20:59 ...Successfully got an update from the \"local\" chart repository\n14:21:00 ...Successfully got an update from the \"stable\" chart repository\n14:21:00 Update Complete. ?Happy Helming!?\n14:21:00 Saving 1 charts\n14:21:00 Downloading common from repo http://127.0.0.1:8879\n14:21:01 Deleting outdated charts\n14:21:01 ==> Linting pomba\n14:21:01 [INFO] Chart.yaml: icon is recommended\n14:21:01 \n14:21:01 1 chart(s) linted, no failures\n14:21:01 Successfully packaged chart and saved it to: /w/workspace/oom-master-verify-helm/kubernetes/dist/packages/pomba-2.0.0.tgz\n14:21:01 make[1]: Leaving directory '/w/workspace/oom-master-verify-helm/kubernetes'\n14:21:01 \n\n\n\tThe merge-helm was the issue - \nhttps://jenkins.onap.org/job/oom-master-merge-helm/29/console\n\n19:18:56 make[1]: Entering directory '/w/workspace/oom-master-merge-helm/kubernetes'\n19:18:57 Error: error unpacking pomba-search-data in pomba: error converting YAML to JSON: yaml: invalid leading UTF-8 octet\n19:18:57 Makefile:42: recipe for target 'dep-pomba' failed\n\n\tLooks like the issue was between the runs – something went in between 14:21 and 19:18 – where the automated merge busted one of the yamls\n/michael",
